{"data":[{"id":563971537,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"88543fd3d285e60a45368e133658ffea","url_token":"yang-xi-17-4","name":"阳曦","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-815cf9158a5c4840ee7864c42bdb4bca_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-815cf9158a5c4840ee7864c42bdb4bca_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/88543fd3d285e60a45368e133658ffea","user_type":"people","headline":"爱慧求真。学问笃实生光辉。人生冒险家，一生追求自由，追寻真理。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":341,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563971537","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546316672,"updated_time":1546344913,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e这位高中生显然不懂什么叫“数学证明”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他的所谓“证明”不是真正的数学证明，所以也谈不上对错。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e之前他的老师还说，他的证明大框架是对的，只是在一些真正能说明问题的细节上写的模糊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个评价。。。如果这位老师真的看过此证明，可见现在的中学数学老师多么缺乏数学素养。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真如他老师所言，那这学生很不错了，毕竟一个高中生搞懂了除去最难部分的内容，也是不易的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大学本科数学首先教学生“什么是真正的数学证明”以及“如何正确的思考一个数学问题”，其次才教如何证明，以及相关知识。没有受过专业训练的人就像这个高中生一样，以为自己在思考，以为自己在证明，实际不是。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e现在的学生啊真浮躁，没几个踏实的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我高中时也是很喜欢数学，很愿意探索现代数学的，但我跟这同学不同，我是一步一步走，他想一步登天。他根本不了解，提出一个全新角度的解法，发明一个新的数学工具，到底有多难。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e什么叫一步一步走？我那时先是提前看完了高二高三数学书，然后做各地高考试卷，模拟卷，尤其做那种高考大省的，出题难的，比如河南，江苏这些。练了一段时间练到什么程度呢？水平已经超过高三学生，基础题看一眼就知道思路答案。后来只看选择题，填空题，大题的最后一题，因为只有这些才有可能难到我了。再后来，连压轴题都无法满足我了，我才想着去看看大学课本。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说的意思不是说必须高考考145+才能去学现代数学，而是应该先把高考搞定再去做更喜欢更有兴趣的东西。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"这位高中生显然不懂什么叫“数学证明”。他的所谓“证明”不是真正的数学证明，所以也谈不上对错。之前他的老师还说，他的证明大框架是对的，只是在一些真正能说明问题的细节上写的模糊。这个评价。。。如果这位老师真的看过此证明，可见现在的中学数学老师…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=74\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%